碧昂斯推出自己的戴维斯爵士威士忌以纪念她的曾祖父https://www.nme.com/news/music/beyonce-launches-her-own-whiskey-sirdavis-in-tribute-to-her-great-grandfather-3785691?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=beyonce-launches-她自己的瑟达维斯威士忌向她的曾祖父致敬Liberty DunworthWed, 21 Aug 2024 15:55:13 +0000 Music NewsNewsCountryPopR&B https://www.nme.com/?p=3785691 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Beyonce@2000x1270-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="碧昂斯在“RENAISSANCE WORLD TOUR”期间登台表演" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Beyonce@2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Beyonce@2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Beyonce@2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Beyonce@2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Beyonce@2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Beyonce@2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>她说，这次冒险的灵感来自于她饮用这款烈酒时感受到的“力量和信心”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/beyonce-launches-her-own-whiskey-sirdavis-in-tribute-to-her-great-grandfather-3785691">碧昂丝推出自己的戴维斯爵士威士忌以向她的曾祖父致敬的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Beyonce@2000x1270-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="碧昂斯在“RENAISSANCE WORLD TOUR”期间登台表演" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Beyonce@2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Beyonce@2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Beyonce@2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Beyonce@2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Beyonce@2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Beyonce@2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beyonce">碧昂斯</a>推出了自己的威士忌品牌，以纪念她的曾祖父。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/beyonce-cowboy-carter-album-review-tracklist-lyrics-3611699">碧昂斯 - 《牛仔卡特》评论：国家重塑收获金币</a></strong></li></ul><p>这款新饮料的品牌名为 SirDavis，以这位歌手的曾祖父戴维斯·霍格 (Davis Hogue) 命名，他是禁酒令时期美国南部的一名农民和私酒贩。</p><p>虽然它是一款美国威士忌，在德克萨斯州完成、混合和装瓶，但它的灵感来自苏格兰威士忌和日本威士忌——歌手是后者的特别粉丝。</p><p>这款烈酒由 51% 黑麦和 49% 大麦混合而成，在雪利酒桶中进行二次熟成，也是 Bey 与酩悦轩尼诗 (Moët Hennessy) 推出的新合作伙伴关系的一部分。</p><p> “我一直被饮用优质威士忌时所感受到的力量和自信所吸引，并希望邀请更多的人体验这种感觉，”碧昂斯在一份新声明中说道（来自<a href="https://www.thelineofbestfit.com/news/in-tribute-to-her-great-grandfather-beyonce-unveils-her-inaugural-whiskey-sirdavis" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Line Of Best Fit</em></a> ）。</p><p> “当我发现我的曾祖父曾经是一个私酒爱好者时，我感觉我对威士忌的热爱是命中注定的。戴维斯爵士是我向他致敬的一种方式，通过新的共同遗产将我们团结在一起，”她补充道。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C-5Ew0Lp2LC/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="displa